msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"Flexplot allows the user to create graphical displays of data, using "
"barcharts and histograms for univariate data, and various different types of "
"scatterplots for bivariate and multivariate data."
msgstr ""
"Flexplot 讓使用者能夠以長條圖與直方圖呈現單變量資料，並以多種不同類型的散佈圖"
"呈現雙變量與多變量資料，進而建立資料的圖形化展示。"

