msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "Input"
msgstr "輸入"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"The variable of interest. This is also called the outcome variable. If only "
"an outcome variable is specified, Flexplot will produce a histogram for "
"numeric data and a barchart for categorical data. If independent variable(s) "
"and/or panelled variable(s) are specified, this variable will be displayed "
"on the Y axis."
msgstr ""
"關注之變項，亦稱為結果變項。若僅指定結果變項，Flexplot 將對數值資料產生直方"
"圖，對類別資料產生長條圖。若有指定自變項及／或分組變項，則此變項將顯示於 Y "
"軸。"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"The variable(s) for which we wish to visually assess relationships with the "
"DV. The first variable chosen shows up on the X axis, either as a "
"scatterplot (for numeric predictors) or as a beeswarm plot (for categorical "
"variables). The second variable chosen will show up as different colors/"
"lines/symbols. If the second varaible chosen is numeric, it will be binned "
"first."
msgstr ""
"欲視覺化評估其與依變項關係之變項。所選之第一個變項將顯示於 X 軸，數值預測變項"
"以散佈圖呈現，類別變項則以蜂群圖呈現。所選之第二個變項將以不同顏色、線條或符"
"號呈現。若第二個變項為數值型，則會先進行分組。"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"Variables specified in these boxes will be binned (if numeric) then "
"displayed as different subplots. The first variable specified as a panelled "
"variable will form the column plots, while the second will form the row "
"plots."
msgstr ""
"於此方框中指定之變項，若為數值型則會先進行分組，再以不同子圖呈現。指定為分組"
"變項之第一個變項將形成欄圖形，第二個變項則形成列圖形。"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "Point controls"
msgstr "資料點控制項"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "The degree of transparency of the dots in the graphics"
msgstr "圖形中資料點之透明度程度"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"The maximal amount of \"jittering\" used on the X axis to remove overlap "
"between datapoints. The maximal amount of jittering is proportional to the "
"density of the data. In other words, the maximum jittering will occur at the "
"mode of the dataset, and little to no jittering will occur in locations "
"where there is no overlap."
msgstr ""
"用於 X 軸上以減少資料點重疊之最大「抖動」量。最大抖動量與資料密度成比例。換言"
"之，最大抖動將發生於資料之眾數處，而在無重疊之區域則幾乎不進行抖動。"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"The maximal amount of \"jittering\" used on the Y axis to remove overlap "
"between datapoints. The maximal amount of jittering is proportional to the "
"density of the data. In other words, the maximum jittering will occur at the "
"mode of the dataset, and little to no jittering will occur in locations "
"where there is no overlap."
msgstr ""
"用於 Y 軸上以減少資料點重疊之最大「抖動」量。最大抖動量與資料密度成比例。換言"
"之，最大抖動將發生於資料之眾數處，而在無重疊之區域則幾乎不進行抖動。"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "Visual Statistics"
msgstr "視覺化統計"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "Should 95% confidence intervals be displayed?"
msgstr "是否應顯示95%的信賴區間？"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "A non-parametric loess line"
msgstr "無母數局部加權迴歸平滑線"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "A straight (regression) line"
msgstr "直線（迴歸）"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"A line that includes both a linear effect and a quadratic (squared) term"
msgstr "同時包含線性效果與二次項（平方項）之曲線"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "A line that includes a linear, squared, and cubed term"
msgstr "包含線性、平方及立方項之曲線"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "No line"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"The type of fitted line displayed when the x axis is a numeric variable. "
"These can be one of the following:"
msgstr "當 X 軸為數值變項時所顯示之配適線類型，可選項目如下："

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"Horizontal lines are displayed at the 25/75th percentiles, with a dot for "
"the median"
msgstr "於第 25／75 百分位數處顯示水平線，並以圓點標示中位數"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"Horizontal lines are displayed at +1/-1 standard deviations from the mean, "
"with a dot for the mean"
msgstr "於平均數正負一個標準差處顯示水平線，並以圓點標示平均數"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "Other Plot Controls"
msgstr "其他圖表控制選項"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"the type of GGplot theme to use when displaying the data. Can be one of the "
"following:"
msgstr "顯示資料時所使用之 GGplot 主題類型，可選項目如下："

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
"Ghost lines are a visual aid that can be used when doing panelled plots. "
"Ghost lines simply repeat the fitted line from one panel across the other "
"panels to make it easier to make comparisons across panels."
msgstr ""
"淡色格線為進行分組繪圖時可使用之視覺輔助工具。淡色格線係將某一子圖中之配適線"
"複製至其他子圖中，以利於跨子圖進行比較。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Descriptives allows the user to obtain basic descriptive statistics, "
"histograms and density plots, correlation plots, boxplots, and frequency "
"tables."
msgstr ""
"描述性統計功能讓使用者得以獲得基本描述性統計量、直方圖與密度圖、相關圖、盒鬚"
"圖及次數分配表。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "References"
msgstr "參照"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "R Packages"
msgstr "R 套件"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Input"
msgstr "輸入"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "All variables of interest."
msgstr "所有感興趣的變量。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Can be split by a categorical variable such as experimental condition."
msgstr "可以按照實驗條件等類別變數進行劃分。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Tranposes the main table"
msgstr "表格轉置"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Percentile Values"
msgstr "百分位數值"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Displays the 25th, 50th, and 75th percentiles of the data points."
msgstr "顯示資料集的第25、第50與第75百分位數。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Cut points for x equal groups"
msgstr "將 x 等分組的切分點"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Displays the cut points that divide the data into x equal groups; default is "
"4 equal groups."
msgstr "顯示將數據分為 x 等分組的切分點；預設為 4 等分組。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Displays the xth percentile; percentile values must be separated by comma."
msgstr "顯示第 x 個百分位數；百分位數值需以逗號分隔。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Central Tendency (only for continuous variables)"
msgstr "集中趨勢（僅適用於連續變數）"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Mode of the data points; if more than one mode exists, only the first is "
"reported. For nominal and ordinal data, the mode is the most frequent "
"observed value. For continuous data, the mode is the value with highest "
"density estimate (see 'Distribution Plots' -> 'Display density'). If a "
"footnote about multimodality for continuous variables is reported, we "
"recommend visualizing the data to check for multimodality."
msgstr ""
"資料點的眾數；若存在多個眾數，則報告第一個就可以了。對於名義變數和次序變數，"
"眾數是出現頻率最高的觀察值。對於連續變數，眾數是密度估計值最高的數值（參見"
"「分布圖」->「顯示密度」）。如果報表中提到連續變數的多峰性相關註解，我們建議"
"視覺化數據以檢查是否存在多峰性。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Median of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的中位數。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Skewness of the distribution of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點分佈曲線的偏斜程度。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Kurtosis of the distribution of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點分佈曲線的尖峰或平坦程度。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Sum of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的總和。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Dispersion (only for continuous variables)"
msgstr "離散程度（僅適用於連續變數）"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Standard deviation of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的標準差。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"The Coefficient of variation gives us the relative dispersion of the data, "
"in contrast to the standard deviation, which gives the absolute dispersion. "
"For this purpose, the standard deviation is divided by the mean value, so "
"that the unit is truncated away."
msgstr ""
"變異係數（Coefficient of variation, CV）提供了數據的相對離散程度，相較於標準"
"差（Standard Deviation），標準差反映的是絕對離散程度。為了計算變異係數，我們"
"將標準差除以平均值，從而消除了\"單位\"的影響。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Median absolute deviation of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的中位數絕對離差 (MAD)。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Median absolute deviation of the data points, adjusted by a factor for "
"asymptotically normal consistency."
msgstr "這是一種經過因素調整以適應漸進常態一致性的中位數絕對離差。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Interquartile range of the data points; 75th percentile - 25th percentile."
msgstr "描述數據點的四分位距；即第 75 百分位數減去第 25 百分位數。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Variance of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的變異數。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Range of the data points; maximum - minimum."
msgstr "描述數據點的分布範圍；即最大值減去最小值。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Minimum value of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的最小值。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Maximum value of the data points."
msgstr "描述資料集中各數據點的最大值。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "width of the confidence interval."
msgstr "信賴區間的寬度(信賴水準)。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"a confidence interval for the standard deviation based on bootstrap samples."
msgstr "基於拔靴樣本之標準差的信賴區間。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "a confidence interval for the variance based on bootstrap samples."
msgstr "基於拔靴樣本之變異數的信賴區間。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "the number of bootstrap samples to be used."
msgstr "將使用之拔靴樣本的樣本數。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Covariance value."
msgstr "顯示共變數的值。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Pearson's correlation coefficient."
msgstr "顯示Pearson相關係數。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "How to deal with missing values?"
msgstr "如何處理遺漏值？"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "use all observations, resulting in NA when there are missing values."
msgstr "使用所有觀察值，當存在遺漏值時，將其設定為 NA。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"missing values are handled by casewise deletion (i.e., only use rows of the "
"data set that are complete)."
msgstr "遺漏值透過逐案刪除法處理（即僅使用資料集中，無遺漏值的個案）。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"use all complete pairs of observations on those variables. This can result "
"in covariance or correlation matrices which are not positive semi-definite."
msgstr ""
"使用這些變量的所有完整配對觀察值。這可能導致共變數或相關矩陣不是正半定"
"(positive semi-definite)的。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"For continuous variables, displays a histogram and the fit of a "
"nonparametric density estimator. For nominal and ordinal variables, displays "
"a frequency distribution."
msgstr ""
"對於連續型變數，顯示長條圖和無母數密度估計的擬合結果；而對於名義型和次序型變"
"數，則顯示頻率分佈。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Displays a matrix of plots between continuous variables, with scatterplots "
"between the variables in the off-diagonal entries, and histograms and "
"density plots in the diagonal entries. The line represents the fit of a 1st, "
"2nd, 3rd, or 4th order polynomial (the selection is based on the Bayesian "
"information criterion; Schwarz, 1978)."
msgstr ""
"顯示連續變量之間的繪圖矩陣，在矩陣的非對角線位置顯示變數之間的散佈圖，而對角"
"線位置上則顯示直方圖和密度圖。該線代表一階、二階、三階或四階多項式的擬合（選"
"擇依據貝氏資訊準則；Schwarz, 1978）。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Displays the counts of each factor/level within the variable in a descending "
"order. The y-axis represents the frequency (counts as grey bars) of each "
"factor/level, the x-axis represents the factors/levels of the variable in an "
"ordered sequence."
msgstr ""
"以遞減順序顯示變項中各因子／水準之計數。Y 軸代表各因子／水準之次數（以灰色長"
"條表示），X 軸代表該變項因子／水準之排序序列。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"By default, a cumulative line is drawn indicating the proportional "
"contribution of each factor. A second vertical axis to the right side of the "
"graph scales with this cumulative line and represents percentages to enable "
"the description of the cumulative line."
msgstr ""
"預設會繪製累積線，以表示各因子之累積貢獻比例。圖形右側之第二垂直軸與此累積線"
"對應，並以百分比呈現，以便描述該累積線。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"If \"Pareto rule\" is enabled, the two new lines enable a more precise "
"assessment of factor/level contribution to the overall contribution (in "
"percent) by using different input numbers."
msgstr ""
"若啟用「柏拉圖法則」，則兩條新增之線條可藉由輸入不同數值，更精確評估因子／水"
"準對整體貢獻度（以百分比計）之影響。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"Displays a horizontally stacked bar chart showing the contribution of levels "
"within a variable in percent. Order of levels depends on defined order in "
"the JASP data table. A legend below the graph provides an overview of levels "
"and their respective colors in the graph."
msgstr ""
"顯示水平堆疊長條圖，以百分比呈現變數內各水準之貢獻度。水準順序取決於 JASP 資"
"料表中定義之順序。圖形下方之圖例提供各水準及其對應顏色之總覽。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"The y-axis represents the variables used, the x-axis represents the "
"percentages. Percentage contribution of all lower-order (below the middle "
"level) and higher-order (above the middle level) levels are displayed on "
"their respective side of the graph."
msgstr ""
"Y 軸代表所使用之變項，X 軸代表百分比。所有較低階層（低於中間水準）與較高階層"
"（高於中間水準）水準之貢獻百分比，分別顯示於圖形之兩側。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"The graph displays percentages on the x-axis as positive in both directions. "
"Reason for the chosen display (in two directions) is the graphs usefulness "
"in survey research where levels often follow a Likert based order (e.g., "
"high - low, likely - unlikely, agreement - disagreement). Therefore, the "
"graph contains a split between levels at their median."
msgstr ""
"圖形將 X 軸之百分比以雙向正值方式呈現。採用此雙向呈現方式之原因，在於該圖形適"
"用於水準常依 Likert 順序（例如：高－低、可能－不可能、同意－不同意）排列之調"
"查研究。因此，圖形在諸水準之中位數處進行分割。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"The number of variable levels determines the number of layers displayed. "
"Layers represent the percentage distribution of the levels of the variable "
"under investigation."
msgstr ""
"變項之水準個數決定所顯示之層數。各層代表所研究變項中各水準之百分比分佈。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"If the variables contain an uneven amount of levels, the middle level is "
"displayed as a grey block in the middle of the stacked bar with its "
"percentage contribution on top."
msgstr ""
"若變項之水準個數為奇數，則中間水準將以灰色區塊顯示於堆疊長條圖之中間，其貢獻"
"百分比則標示於區塊上方。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"For continuous variables, displays a boxplot. Optionally, the outliers are "
"labelled. Outliers are based on the interquartile range (IQR), i.e., [25th "
"percentile] - 1.5 × IQR and [75th percentile] + 1.5 × IQR. Can also display "
"in color, and has selectable boxplot, violin, and jitter elements for "
"displaying the distribution of the data. This can be split by a categorical "
"variable such as experimental condition."
msgstr ""
"針對連續變數，顯示盒鬚圖。可選擇標示極端值。極端值係依據四分位距（IQR）定義，"
"即第 25 百分位數減 1.5 倍 IQR，以及第 75 百分位數加 1.5 倍 IQR。亦可選擇以顏"
"色呈現，並可選用盒鬚圖、小提琴圖及抖動散點等元素來呈現資料分佈。可依類別變數"
"（如實驗條件）進行分組顯示。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Frequency Tables (nominal and ordinal variables)"
msgstr "次數分配表（名義變項與序位變項）"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Displays a frequency table for each variable."
msgstr "顯示各變數之次數分配表。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Displays the spread of a variable."
msgstr "顯示變項之分佈情形。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Stem: the first digit(s)."
msgstr "莖：第一位（或前幾位）數字。"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid "Leaf: the first digit after the stem."
msgstr "葉：莖之後的第一位數字。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"The output is a raincloud plot for each dependent variable. Optionally, "
"there is a table with statistics for each plot."
msgstr "輸出結果為每個依變項之雨雲圖。另可選擇輸出每個圖形對應之統計量表格。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"How can I re-use my elaborate, customized plot settings for a different "
"dataset?"
msgstr "如何將我精心設定之自訂圖形選項套用至不同的資料集？"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Suppose that you have two datasets A and B (in separate JASP files) for "
"which you want to create the same raincloud plot.<br>Further, suppose that "
"you already have a raincloud plot for dataset A and now you want the same "
"one for dataset B.<br>There are two ways in which you can achieve this "
"without having to specify the custom plot settings all over again."
msgstr ""
"假設您有兩個資料集 A 與 B（分別儲存於不同 JASP 檔案中），且希望為兩者建立相同"
"之雨雲圖。<br>再假設您已為資料集 A 建立好雨雲圖，現在希望為資料集 B 建立相同"
"之圖形。<br>有兩種方式可達成此目的，而無需重新設定所有自訂圖形選項。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"1) If dataset B only has a different dependent variable but is otherwise "
"identical,<br>then you can copy and paste this variable from the JASP file "
"for dataset B into the JASP file for dataset A (see Edit Data header menu in "
"JASP).<br>Next, select the newly created dependent variable in dataset A as "
"an additional dependent variable for the raincloud plot."
msgstr ""
"1) 若資料集 B 僅依變項不同，其餘結構完全相同，<br>則可將資料集 B 之 JASP 檔案"
"中的該變項複製並貼入資料集 A 之 JASP 檔案中（請參閱 JASP 中「編輯資料」標題選"
"單）。<br>接著，在資料集 A 中選取此新建之依變項，作為雨雲圖之額外依變項。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"2) If dataset B is rather different from dataset A<br>(e.g. primary factor "
"has different name and additional levels or there are fewer observations "
"with different IDs),<br>then you have to take a different approach."
"<br>First, make a copy of the JASP file for dataset A (called target file in "
"the following).<br>Second, open this target file. It should show the "
"raincloud plot as specified for dataset A.<br>Third, go to the Edit Data "
"header menu and _delete the entire dataset A_.<br>Fourth, go to the JASP "
"file for dataset B and copy-paste its data to the target file.<br>Fifth, "
"choose the dependent variables, primary and secondary factor, covariate, and "
"ID for the raincloud plot.<br>Importantly, though, all the other "
"specifications like point spread or custom interval limits should still be "
"present from the raincloud plot for dataset A."
msgstr ""
"2) 若資料集 B 與資料集 A 差異較大<br>（例如：主要因子名稱不同或新增水準，或觀"
"察值較少且 ID 不同），<br>則需採用不同之處理方式。<br>首先，複製資料集 A 之 "
"JASP 檔案（以下稱為目標檔案）。<br>第二，開啟此目標檔案。此時應顯示為資料集 "
"A 所設定之雨雲圖。<br>第三，前往「編輯資料」標題選單，並 _刪除整個資料集 A_。"
"<br>第四，開啟資料集 B 之 JASP 檔案，將其資料複製並貼入目標檔案中。<br>第五，"
"選取雨雲圖所需之依變項、主要因子、次要因子、共變量及 ID。<br>重點在於，資料"
"集 A 雨雲圖中所有其他設定（如資料點散佈程度或自訂區間界限）應仍保留於目標檔案"
"中。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "References"
msgstr "參照"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Input"
msgstr "輸入"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Dependent Variables"
msgstr "依變項"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Select all the variables that you want to plot."
msgstr "選取您欲繪圖之所有變項。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Primary Factor"
msgstr "主要因子"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Its levels are shown on the x-axis (y-axis for horizontal plot)."
msgstr "其各水準顯示於 X 軸（水平繪圖時則為 Y 軸）。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Secondary Factor"
msgstr "次要因子"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Its levels are color coded."
msgstr "其各水準以顏色標示。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Covariate"
msgstr "共變量"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Points are color coded according to this."
msgstr "資料點依此變項進行顏色編碼。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "ID"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Select a participant/observation ID in your dataset, to connect individual "
"observations (points) accross the levels of the primary factor. Otherwise, "
"you do not need this."
msgstr ""
"選取資料集中之參與者／觀察值 ID，以連結主要因子各水準下之個別觀察值（資料"
"點）。若無此需求，則可不選。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "General"
msgstr "一般設定"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Color palette"
msgstr "調色盤"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "How to color code the levels of the secondary factor."
msgstr "如何為次要因子的水準進行顏色編碼。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Covariate palette"
msgstr "共變量調色盤"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"How to color code the covariate. 'Viridis' works good for both discrete and "
"continuous covariates."
msgstr "共變量之顏色編碼方式。「Viridis」色板適用於離散型與連續型共變量。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Apply color palette to primary factor"
msgstr "將調色盤應用於主要因子"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Applies the color palette to the levels of the primary factor. Otherwise, "
"the plot stays black and white.<br>This option is superseeded by a secondary "
"factor; then color coding is according to that."
msgstr ""
"將色彩調色盤套用至主要因子的各層級。否則，圖表將保持黑白顯示。<br>若有次要因"
"子存在，則此選項會被覆蓋，顏色編碼將依次要因子設定。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Horizontal plot"
msgstr "水平作圖"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Plots the dependent variable axis horizontally, at the bottom of the plot."
"<br>This is where the raincloud plot gets its name from: It will look like "
"the points are raining from the violin and box (cloud)."
msgstr ""
"將依變項軸繪製於圖形底部之水平方向。<br>此即雨雲圖名稱之由來：資料點看起來如"
"同從小提琴圖與盒鬚圖（雲）中落下之雨滴。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Table with statistics"
msgstr "附帶統計數據的表格"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Shows a table under the plot with statistics per cloud, like number of "
"observations or median.<br>If you select 'Mean' or 'Interval around "
"mean' (see Advanced Section), they will also be shown here."
msgstr ""
"於圖形下方顯示每個雲之統計量表格，例如觀察值個數或中位數。<br>若您選取「平均"
"數」或「平均數區間」（請參閱進階區段），這些統計量亦會顯示於此。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Shows the box statistics in the table: lower whisker, 25th percentile, "
"median, 75th percentile, upper whisker.<br>It can be helpful to un-check "
"this if you are also working with 'Interval around mean' (see Advanced "
"Section)."
msgstr ""
"於表格中顯示盒鬚圖統計量：下鬚、第 25 百分位數、中位數、第 75 百分位數、上"
"鬚。<br>若同時使用「平均數區間」（請參閱進階區段），取消勾選此項可能有所幫"
"助。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Cloud Elements"
msgstr "雲圖元素設定"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Show violin"
msgstr "顯示小提琴圖"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Whether or not the violin should be shown. If un-checked, opacity is set to "
"0 and outline to 'none'."
msgstr "是否顯示小提琴圖。若取消勾選，透明度將設為 0，邊框則設為「無」。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Show box"
msgstr "顯示箱形圖"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Whether or not the box should be shown. If un-checked, opacity is set to 0 "
"and outline to 'none'.<br>An interval around the mean disables the box "
"altogether."
msgstr ""
"是否顯示盒鬚圖。若取消勾選，透明度將設為 0，邊框則設為「無」。<br>選取平均數"
"區間時，盒鬚圖將完全停用。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Whether or not the points of a cloud should be shown. If un-checked, opacity "
"is set to 0.<br>If you have many, many points, it can be helpful to hide "
"them."
msgstr ""
"是否顯示雲之資料點。若取消勾選，透明度將設為 0。<br>若資料點數量極多，隱藏資"
"料點可能有所幫助。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Element Settings"
msgstr "元素設定"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Nudge"
msgstr "微調位置"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"The nudge for violin, box, and point determines how far the elements are "
"nudged from the center (axis tick).<br>By default, the box is in the center "
"(nudge = 0) and the violin is nudged to the right. The points are nudged to "
"the left of the box.<br>With a custom orientation (see Advanced section), "
"the points get centered (nudge fixed to 0). Violin and box are nudged "
"depending on orientation: left or right."
msgstr ""
"小提琴圖、盒鬚圖與資料點之偏移量，決定各元素自中心（軸刻度）偏移之距離。<br>"
"預設情況下，盒鬚圖位於中心（偏移量 = 0），小提琴圖向右偏移，資料點則向左偏移"
"至盒鬚圖左側。<br>若採用自訂方向（請參閱進階區段），資料點將置中（偏移量固定"
"為 0），小提琴圖與盒鬚圖則依方向向左或向右偏移。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Height, Width, and Spread"
msgstr "高度、寬度與散佈程度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"These settings determine the respective properties of the elements:"
"<br><br>How high should the violin peak? (Does not change the proportions of "
"the probability density.)<br>With a custom orientation to the left (see "
"Advanced Section), it can be helpful to decrease the height if the violin "
"overlaps with axis ticks.<br><br>How wide should the box be?<br><br>How wide "
"should the points spread? I.e., how jittered should they be along the x-axis "
"(y-axis if horizontal plot?.<br>Note, that this still correctly shows the "
"values of the points on the dependent variable axis.<br>(If you would also "
"like y-jitter see the 'Jitter' option for points.)"
msgstr ""
"這些設定決定元素之相應屬性：<br><br>小提琴圖之峰值應多高？（不改變機率密度之"
"比例。）<br>若採用向左之自訂方向（請參閱進階區段），當小提琴圖與軸刻度重疊"
"時，降低高度可能有所幫助。<br><br>盒鬚圖之寬度應為多少？<br><br>資料點之散佈"
"程度應多寬？亦即，資料點沿 X 軸（水平繪圖時則為 Y 軸）之抖動程度應為何？<br>"
"請注意，此設定仍能正確顯示資料點在依變項軸上之數值。<br>（若亦需要 Y 軸抖動，"
"請參閱資料點之「抖動」選項。）"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Box Padding"
msgstr "盒鬚圖內縮距離"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"With a secondary factor, there will be a box for each factor level. With the "
"padding, you can change the spacing between theses boxes.<br>Increasing the "
"padding will - visually - decrease the box width. If you want to keep box "
"width constant, also increase the box width."
msgstr ""
"若有次要因子，則每個因子水準將各自對應一個盒鬚圖。透過內縮距離，可調整這些盒"
"鬚圖之間距。<br>增加內縮距離在視覺上會減小盒鬚圖之寬度。若希望保持盒鬚圖寬度"
"不變，請同時增加盒鬚圖之寬度。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Point Size"
msgstr "資料點大小"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "We recommend a greater size, the fewer points you have."
msgstr "資料點越少，建議使用越大之尺寸。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Opacity"
msgstr "透明度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Increase this to _decrease_ the transparency of the respective element."
msgstr "增加此值將 _降低_ 該元素之透明度。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Outline and Outline Width"
msgstr "輪廓線與輪廓線寬度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Would you like the outline to match the 'Color palette', be 'black', or have "
"'none' at all?<br>The width determines how thick the outline is."
msgstr ""
"您希望邊框與「色彩調色盤」一致、為「黑色」，還是完全「無邊框」？<br>寬度則決"
"定邊框的粗細。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Violin Smoothing"
msgstr "小提琴圖平滑程度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"This percentage determines the smoothness of the probability density.<br>The "
"lower, the stronger it is influenced by the presence/absence of individual "
"points."
msgstr ""
"此百分比決定機率密度之平滑程度。<br>數值越低，平滑程度越容易受個別資料點之有"
"無影響。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Point Jitter"
msgstr "資料點抖動"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Use this with care!<br>It slightly jitters the points along the dependent "
"variable axis. This means that the position of the points no longer matches "
"the values of the observations.<br>If you want to have less overlap between "
"the points while keeping an accurate visualization, increases the point "
"spread.<br>Using point jitter can be useful in some cases. For example, if "
"you are working with likert data."
msgstr ""
"請謹慎使用此功能！<br>此功能會將資料點沿依變項軸進行輕微抖動，這表示資料點之"
"位置將不再對應於觀察值之實際數值。<br>若希望在保持準確視覺化之同時減少資料點"
"重疊，請增加資料點散佈程度。<br>在某些情況下，使用資料點抖動仍可能有所幫助，"
"例如處理 Likert 量表資料時。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "ID Lines Width"
msgstr "ID 連線寬度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Determines how thick the lines are."
msgstr "決定線條之粗細。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Violin"
msgstr "小提琴外觀"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Height"
msgstr "高度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Outline"
msgstr "輪廓"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "black"
msgstr "黑色"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "none"
msgstr "無"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Outline width"
msgstr "輪廓寬度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Smoothing"
msgstr "平滑度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Box"
msgstr "箱形外觀"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Width"
msgstr "寬度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Padding"
msgstr "內邊距"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Point"
msgstr "點圖外觀"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Spread"
msgstr "散布範圍"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Size"
msgstr "點的大小"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Jitter"
msgstr "輕微偏移"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "ID lines"
msgstr "ID線"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Axes, Caption, and Plot Size"
msgstr "座標軸、標題和圖表大小的設定"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Custom limits for dependent variable axis:"
msgstr "設定依變數軸(縱軸)的範圍："

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Use this with care!<br>If your dataset has observations that lie outside of "
"the specified, the plot will be truncated and it will not show these "
"observations.<br>The limits you specify may only be applied approximately. "
"For further fine-tuning of the axis, click the title of the plot where it "
"says the name of dependent variable.<br>Then select 'Edit Image' in the drop "
"down menu and then go to the headers 'x-axis' or 'y-axis'."
msgstr ""
"使用時請小心！<br> 如果資料集中的觀測值超出了指定的範圍，圖表將被截斷，並且這"
"些觀測值將不再顯示。<br> 你指定的範圍可能僅會近似應用。如果需要進一步微調坐標"
"軸，可以點擊圖表標題中顯示依變數名稱的部分。<br> 然後在下拉式功能表中選擇“編"
"輯統計圖”，然後再去進行“x 軸”或“y 軸”的設定。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "from"
msgstr "從"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "to"
msgstr "到"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Limits may only be applied approximately.\n"
"For further fine-tuning of the axis, click the title of the plot\n"
"where it says the name of dependent variable.\n"
"Then select 'Edit Image' in the drop down menu and\n"
"then go to the headers 'x-axis' or 'y-axis'."
msgstr ""
"界限可能僅能近似套用。\n"
"如需進一步微調軸線，請點選圖形標題處\n"
"顯示依變項名稱之位置。\n"
"接著於下拉選單中選取「編輯圖像」，\n"
"再前往「X 軸」或「Y 軸」標題處進行調整。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Show caption"
msgstr "顯示標題"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"The caption provides important information about the plot such as warnings, "
"if there are any.<br>We strongly recommend to leave this checkbox checked "
"and to only un-check it if you are otherwise happy with the plot and want to "
"export it."
msgstr ""
"標題提供關於圖表的重要資訊，例如警告（如果有的話）。<br>我們強烈建議保留該核"
"取方塊的勾選狀態，只有在您對圖表滿意並且想要匯出時，才取消勾選。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Plot Size: Width and Height"
msgstr "圖的尺寸：寬度和高度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"This also includes the legend (if there is color coding) and the caption."
"<br>While you can also change the size of a JASP plot with your mouse, the "
"precise specification of width and height allows you to exactly reproduce a "
"plot."
msgstr ""
"這也包括圖例（如果有顏色編碼）和標題。<br>雖然你也可以透過滑鼠調整 JASP 圖表"
"的尺寸，但設定寬度和高度，可以確保圖表的精確度。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Plot Size"
msgstr "圖的尺寸"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Advanced"
msgstr "進階設定"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Mean"
msgstr "平均數"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Whether to also show a mean for each cloud."
msgstr "是否要顯示每個數據雲的平均數。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Position"
msgstr "位置"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Use a 'Custom' position to have the mean placed inside of the box - even if "
"you do not show the box.<br>In fact, the mean nudge and distance fields are "
"synchronized with the box nudge and box fields, respectively.<br>Use the 'On "
"axis ticks' position to have all means for each primary factor level on top "
"of each other.<br>This can be useful if you want to show the change of "
"secondary factor levels (e.g. groups) across the primary factor levels (e.g. "
"time)."
msgstr ""
"使用「自定義」位置可以將平均數放置在箱形圖內——即使您不顯示箱形圖。實際上，平"
"均數位置的微調和距離欄位與箱形圖的微調和箱形圖的欄位是同步的。<br>使用“在軸刻"
"度上”位置，則可以將每個主因素水準的所有平均數放置在彼此的頂部。這在您想要展示"
"次要因素水準（例如不同組別）隨主要因素水準（例如時間）變化時非常有用。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Try different values to make your plot especially pretty."
msgstr "嘗試不同數值，使您的圖形更加美觀。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Mean Lines: Width"
msgstr "平均數線：寬度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "See outline width of box and violin as well as ID lines width."
msgstr "請參閱盒鬚圖與小提琴圖之輪廓線寬度，以及 ID 連線寬度。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Custom"
msgstr "自定義"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Distance"
msgstr "距離"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "On axis ticks"
msgstr "在軸刻度上"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Connect means with lines"
msgstr "以直線連接各平均數"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Interval around mean"
msgstr "平均數周圍的區間"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Whether to also show an interval around the mean.<br>This hides and disables "
"the box."
msgstr "是否顯示平均數周圍的區間。這將隱藏並禁用箱形圖。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Confidence interval"
msgstr "信賴區間"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Interval line width"
msgstr "區間線寬度"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Determines the thickness of the interval lines."
msgstr "設定區間線的粗細。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Width of interval whiskers depends on mean distance."
msgstr "區間鬍鬚的寬度，取決於平均數距離。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Custom Cloud Orientation, Mean Interval Limits, and Cloud Color"
msgstr "自訂雲圖方向、平均數區間限制和雲圖顏色"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "How many clouds are currently shown?"
msgstr "目前顯示了多少個雲圖？"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"To apply custom cloud orientation or custom mean intervals, you first must "
"specify the number of clouds that are currently shown in the plot.<br>If the "
"number you entered does not match the number of clouds in the plot, the plot "
"caption will show a warning and you can correct your entry.<br>The number "
"you specify determines the number of rows in the table."
msgstr ""
"若要套用自訂之雲方向或自訂平均數區間，您必須先指定圖形中目前顯示之雲的數量。"
"<br>若輸入之數量與圖形中雲的數量不符，圖形標題處將顯示警告，屆時您可修正輸入"
"值。<br>所指定之數量將決定表格中列數之多寡。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"In the table, you can then specify the custom orientation ('L' vs. 'R') for "
"each cloud as well as custom lower and upper interval limits for each mean."
"<br>Make sure to also check the corresponding checkboxes 'Apply custom "
"orientation' or 'Apply custom mean interval limits'.<br>Otherwise, your "
"input into the table will not be applied."
msgstr ""
"於表格中，您可為每個雲指定自訂方向（「L」代表左，「R」代表右），以及每個平均"
"數之自訂區間下限與上限。<br>請務必同時勾選對應之核取方塊「套用自訂方向」或"
"「套用自訂平均數區間界限」。<br>否則，您在表格中之輸入將不會被套用。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"The order in which the rows of the table are mapped to the clouds in the "
"plot is as follows:<br>Suppose, there are three times of measurement "
"(primary factor): pre, post, and follow-up.<br>Further, there are two "
"species (secondary factor): alpha and beta.<br>This means that there are 6 "
"clouds, in the following order:<br>pre-alpha<br>pre-beta<br>post-"
"alpha<br>post-beta<br>follow-up-alpha<br>follow-up-beta<br><br>In this "
"example you could now specify the odd rows as 'L' and the even rows as 'R'."
"<br>That way, at each time point, the left cloud would be alpha and the "
"right cloud would be beta."
msgstr ""
"表格中各列對應至圖形中各雲之順序如下：<br>假設有三個測量時間點（主要因子）："
"前測、後測與追蹤。<br>另有兩個物種（次要因子）：alpha 與 beta。<br>此表示共"
"有 6 個雲，其順序如下：<br>前測-alpha<br>前測-beta<br>後測-alpha<br>後測-"
"beta<br>追蹤-alpha<br>追蹤-beta<br><br>在此範例中，您可以將奇數列指定為"
"「L」，偶數列指定為「R」。<br>如此一來，在每個時間點上，左側之雲即為 alpha，"
"右側之雲即為 beta。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"If you have a 2x2 design (e.g. no follow-up in as primary factor), then a "
"useful custom orientation could be LLRR.<br>That way, both the alpha and the "
"beta cloud at time point pre would be left and at time point they would be "
"right.<br>Combine this with ID input to connect the individual observations "
"over time.<br>They will then run between the two clouds on the left to the "
"two clouds on the right."
msgstr ""
"若為 2x2 設計（例如主要因子中無追蹤測量），則實用之自訂方向可設為 LLRR。<br>"
"如此一來，前測時間點之 alpha 雲與 beta 雲均位於左側，而後測時間點則均位於右"
"側。<br>將此設定與 ID 輸入相結合，可連結個別觀察值在不同時間點之變化。<br>屆"
"時連線將從左側兩個雲之間延伸至右側兩個雲之間。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Any custom orientation or mean intervals will be applied to the plot of "
"every dependent variable.<br>How can you specify different custom mean "
"intervals for two dependent variables?<br>For this, you can duplicate the "
"analysis (see symbol: white plus on green background),<br>only select one "
"dependent variable in each version, and specify the custom intervals "
"separately."
msgstr ""
"任何自訂方向或平均數區間將套用至每個依變項之圖形。<br>若要為兩個依變項分別指"
"定不同之自訂平均數區間，該如何處理？<br>為此，您可以複製分析（請參閱綠色背景"
"上之白色加號符號），<br>於每個版本中僅選取一個依變項，並分別指定自訂區間。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"For custom cloud colors, just enter the hexcode you want. This features only "
"works when there is no Secondary Factor."
msgstr ""
"若要自訂雲之顏色，請直接輸入所需之十六進位色碼。此功能僅在無次要因子時方可使"
"用。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Apply custom orientation"
msgstr "運用自定義方向"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Apply custom mean interval limits"
msgstr "運用自定義的平均數區間限制"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Apply custom colors"
msgstr "運用自定義的顏色"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Cloud"
msgstr "雲"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Orientation"
msgstr "方向"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Lower Limit"
msgstr "下限"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Upper Limit"
msgstr "上限"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Color"
msgstr "顏色"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"For customization, the cloud order is as follows:\n"
"For each level of the Primary Factor,\n"
"go through all levels of the Secondary Factor.\n"
"For example, with a 2 (Primary: X, Y) x 2 (Secondary: i, ii) design,\n"
"there are four clouds, A to D, with:\n"
"A = Xi, B = Xii, C = Yi, D = Yii.\n"
"\n"
"Custom orientation:\n"
"Per default, all violins are right of the boxes.\n"
"To customize this, specify 'L' or 'R' for each cloud.\n"
"Applying the custom orientation sets Point Nudge to 0.\n"
"\n"
"Custom Color:\n"
"Specify a hexcode. Only works when there is no Secondary Factor."
msgstr ""
"關於自訂，雲之順序如下：\n"
"針對主要因子之每個水準，\n"
"依序遍歷次要因子之所有水準。\n"
"例如，在 2（主要因子：X, Y）× 2（次要因子：i, ii）設計中，\n"
"共有四個雲，編號 A 至 D，分別為：\n"
"A = Xi, B = Xii, C = Yi, D = Yii。\n"
"\n"
"自訂方向：\n"
"預設情況下，所有小提琴圖均位於盒鬚圖之右側。\n"
"若要自訂此設定，請為每個雲指定「L」或「R」。\n"
"套用自訂方向時，資料點偏移量將設為 0。\n"
"\n"
"自訂顏色：\n"
"請指定十六進位色碼。僅在無次要因子時方可使用。"

#, qt-format
msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"How should the confidence interval be computed? By default, we use a `T "
"model`, which yields results identical to a one-sample t-test. Alternative "
"options are a normal model (%1), or `Bootstrap`."
msgstr ""
"信賴區間應該如何計算？預設情況下，我們使用「T 分配」，其結果與單一樣本 t 檢定"
"相同。其他選項包括「常態模型」(%1)或「拔靴法(Bootstrap)」。"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid "95% confidende intervals"
msgstr "95% 信賴區間"

msgctxt "FlexplotForm|"
msgid ""
