msgstr "顯示水平線標示平均數的95%信賴區間"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Show legend"
msgstr "顯示圖例"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid ""
"Shows the legend for the color-coding of the primary factor.<br>This option "
"is superseeded by a secondary factor; then the legend is always added."
msgstr ""
"顯示主要因子顏色對應之圖例。<br>此選項在設有次要因子時將被取代；屆時圖例將一"
"律顯示。"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Show points"
msgstr "顯示點圖"

msgctxt "raincloudPlots|"
msgid "Standard error"
msgstr "標準誤"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
msgid ""
"How should the confidence interval be computed? By default, we use an "
"analytical approach (chi-square). The alternative option is `Bootstrap`"
msgstr ""
"信賴區間應該如何計算？預設情況下，我們使用的分析方法為卡方法。替代選項是「拔"
"靴法」"

msgctxt "Descriptives|"
