msgstr "選取此項以建立非重複測量圖形"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Select this to create a repeated-measures plot"
msgstr "選取此項以建立重複測量圖形"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"ON (listwise deletion): if a case is missing even one of the selected "
"variables, the whole case is excluded.OFF: keep every case and ignore only "
"the specific values that are missing"
msgstr ""
"ON（完整刪除）：若某一案例在選取之變項中至少有一項缺失，則該整個案例將被排"
"除。OFF：保留所有案例，僅忽略特定缺失之數值"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Delete missing values listwise"
msgstr "以完全排除法處理缺失值"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Input for non-repeated measures plot"
msgstr "非重複測量圖形之輸入設定"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Select the variable for the X-Axis"
msgstr "選取 X 軸之變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Select the variable for the Y-Axis"
msgstr "選取 Y 軸之變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Select the variable for data grouping, which will also determine the "
"coloring."
msgstr "選取資料分組之變項，此變項亦將決定顏色區分。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "You can choose a variable to split the plots into columns"
msgstr "可選取一個變項，將圖形分割為多欄顯示"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "You can choose a variable to split the plots into rows"
msgstr "可選取一個變項，將圖形分割為多列顯示"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "You can choose a variable to make a grid"
msgstr "可選取一個變項以建立網格"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Input for repeated measures plot"
msgstr "重複測量圖形之輸入設定"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Here you can specify the factor for the repeated measures. For example, it "
"could be time (e.g., 24 h, 48 h, 72 h) or conditions like before and after"
msgstr ""
"此處可指定重複測量之因子。例如，可為時間（如 24 小時、48 小時、72 小時）或實"
"驗前後等條件"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Assign the variables that correspond to each level of the repeated measures "
"factor. For example, if the factor is time, assign variables like '24h', "
"'48h', and '72h'"
msgstr ""
"指派對應於重複測量因子各水準之變項。例如，若因子為時間，則指派如「24h」、"
"「48h」及「72h」等變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Select the between-subject factors that distinguish different groups of "
"subjects, such as treatment group, gender, or genotype. These variables must "
"be categorical (nominal) with at least two levels"
msgstr ""
"選取可區分不同受試者組別之受試者間因子，例如實驗處理組別、性別或基因型。這些"
"變項必須為具有至少兩個水準之類別變項（名義變項）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Select continuous variables that may influence the outcome and should be "
"included as covariates in the analysis"
msgstr "選取可能影響結果之連續變項，並將其作為共變量納入分析"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Select the variable for data grouping, which will also determine the coloring"
msgstr "選取資料分組之變項，此變項亦將決定顏色區分"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Check this option to show individual data points on the plot"
msgstr "勾選此選項以在圖形上顯示個別資料點"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Set the point size"
msgstr "設定資料點大小"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Size by variable"
msgstr "依變項調整大小"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Choose this if you want the point size to be determined by a variable rather "
"than a fixed constant"
msgstr "若希望資料點大小由變項決定而非固定常數，請選擇此項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Shape by variable"
msgstr "依變項調整形狀"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Choose this if you want the point shape to be determined by a variable"
msgstr "若希望資料點形狀由變項決定，請選擇此項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Set the transparency"
msgstr "設定透明度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Adjusts the horizontal “dodge” spacing between subgroup geometric elements. "
"Only takes effect when a grouping variable is mapped (e.g., male vs. female "
"within each species). A value of 0 overlays the elements; higher values push "
"the subgroups farther apart"
msgstr ""
"調整子群組幾何物件之間的水平「並排」間距。僅在已對應分組變項（例如各物種內之"
"雄性與雌性）時生效。數值為 0 時各元素重疊；數值越大，子群組間距離越遠"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add a black outline/border to the elements"
msgstr "為幾何物件添加黑色輪廓線／邊框"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "White outline"
msgstr "白色輪廓線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add a white outline/border to the elements"
msgstr "為幾何物件添加白色輪廓線／邊框"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Remove the fill"
msgstr "移除填充顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Point Size Variable"
msgstr "資料點大小變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Min point size"
msgstr "最小資料點尺寸"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Max point size"
msgstr "最大資料點尺寸"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Point Shape Variable"
msgstr "資料點形狀變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add ellipse"
msgstr "添加橢圓"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Add a statistical ellipse around the points.'Ellipse type' controls the "
"method:\"t\" assumes a multivariate t-distribution,\"Normal\" assumes a "
"multivariate normal distribution,and \"Euclidean\" draws a circle whose "
"radius equals the value of 'Level'"
msgstr ""
"在資料點周圍添加統計橢圓。「橢圓類型」控制計算方法：\"t\" 假設多變量 t 分"
"配，\"Normal\" 假設多變量常態分配，\"Euclidean\" 則繪製半徑等於「水準」數值之"
"圓形"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Ellipse type"
msgstr "橢圓類型"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "t"
msgstr ""

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Normal"
msgstr "常態"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Euclidean"
msgstr "歐幾里得"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Level"
msgstr "水準"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Confidence level (for t and normal ellipse type) or radius (euclidean "
"ellipse type)"
msgstr "信賴水準（適用於 t 與常態橢圓類型）或半徑（適用於歐氏距離橢圓類型）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Sets the number of bins used to divide the data range in histograms.More "
"bins give finer detail, fewer bins give a more general overview"
msgstr ""
"設定直方圖中用於分割資料範圍之區間數。區間數越多可呈現更細緻之細節，區間數越"
"少則提供更整體之概觀"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Density"
msgstr "密度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Check this option to overlay a density estimate on the histogram. Density "
"can be shown as scaled (0–1) or on the histogram count scale."
msgstr ""
"勾選此選項以在直方圖上疊加密度估計值。密度可以標準化形式（0–1）或原始直方圖計"
"數尺度呈現。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Density overlay mode"
msgstr "密度疊加模式"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Choose whether the density curve is scaled to the histogram count ('Count'), "
"or normalized to a maximum of 1 ('Scaled')"
msgstr ""
"選擇密度曲線是縮放至直方圖計數（「計數」），還是正規化至最大值為 1（「標準"
"化」）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Show density on the histogram count scale (area under the curve equals total "
"count)"
msgstr "以直方圖計數尺度顯示密度（曲線下面積等於總計數）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Scaled (0–1)"
msgstr "標準化（0–1）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Show density scaled so that the maximum of the curve is 1"
msgstr "顯示密度曲線，並將其最大值縮放為 1"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Set the transparency for the density overlay"
msgstr "設定密度疊加圖層之透明度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Set the line width for the density overlay"
msgstr "設定密度疊加圖層之線條寬度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Check this option to create boxplot. Boxplot and violin plot require both X-"
"Axis and Y-Axis variables."
msgstr "勾選此選項以建立盒鬚圖。盒鬚圖與小提琴圖皆需要 X 軸與 Y 軸變項。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Sets the line width of the geometric element (e.g., boxplot, violin, error "
"bar). Increase for thicker outlines, decrease for thinner ones"
msgstr ""
"設定幾何物件（例如盒鬚圖、小提琴圖、誤差線）之線條寬度。數值增加可使輪廓線變"
"粗，數值減少則變細"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Set the width of the boxplots"
msgstr "設定盒鬚圖之寬度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Sets the horizontal width of the whiskers in a boxplot"
msgstr "設定盒鬚圖中鬚線之水平寬度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Displays individual outlier points beyond the whiskers in a boxplot. "
"Outliers are defined as values that fall outside the range of Q1 − coef × "
"IQR and Q3 + coef × IQR"
msgstr ""
"於盒鬚圖中顯示超出鬚線範圍之個別離異值。離異值定義為落在 Q1 − coef × IQR 與 "
"Q3 + coef × IQR 範圍以外之數值"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Sets the multiplier (coef) used to define outliers in a boxplot. Outliers "
"are values beyond Q1 − coef × IQR or Q3 + coef × IQR"
msgstr ""
"設定盒鬚圖中用於定義離異值之乘數（coef）。離異值為超出 Q1 − coef × IQR 或 Q3 "
"+ coef × IQR 之數值"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Set the size of the outliers"
msgstr "設定離異值之大小"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Controls how the width of each violin is scaled:<b>Area</b>: all violins "
"have the same area (default in ggplot2).<b>Count</b>: violins are scaled by "
"the number of observations in each group.<b>Width</b>: all violins have the "
"same maximum width, regardless of group size."
msgstr ""
"控制各小提琴圖之寬度縮放方式：<b>面積</b>：所有小提琴圖具有相同面積（ggplot2 "
"預設值）。<b>計數</b>：小提琴圖依各組觀察值個數進行縮放。<b>寬度</b>：無論組"
"別大小，所有小提琴圖具有相同之最大寬度。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Draws horizontal lines at the specified quantiles inside each violin. Use "
"comma-separated values between 0 and 1 (e.g., 0.25, 0.5, 0.75) to show "
"quartiles or other custom quantiles."
msgstr ""
"在各小提琴圖內部之指定分位數處繪製水平線。請使用介於 0 與 1 之間以逗號分隔之"
"數值（例如 0.25, 0.5, 0.75）來顯示四分位數或其他自訂分位數。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"If checked, the violins are trimmed to the range of the data. If unchecked, "
"the density tails may extend beyond the observed values."
msgstr ""
"若勾選此項，小提琴圖將修剪至資料範圍內。若未勾選，密度之尾端可能延伸至觀察值"
"範圍之外。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"This section adds layers that visualise amounts. <b>Dodge</b> shifts "
"subgroup geoms sideways so they don’t overlap. <b>Size / Width</b> sets the "
"thickness of bars and lines or the radius of dots. <b>Transparency (alpha)</"
"b> controls opacity: 0 = invisible, 1 = solid. <b>Outline (black / white)</"
"b> toggles a border around the shape. "
msgstr ""
"本區段新增用於視覺化數量之圖層。<b>並排</b>將子群組幾何物件橫向偏移，以避免重"
"疊。<b>尺寸／寬度</b>設定長條與線條之粗細，或圓點之半徑。<b>透明度（alpha）</"
"b>控制不透明度：0 = 完全透明，1 = 完全不透明。<b>輪廓線（黑色／白色）</b>切換"
"形狀周圍之邊框。 "

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Enable to add dashed lines to the plot"
msgstr "啟用此選項以在圖形中新增虛線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Enable to add count dots to the plot"
msgstr "啟用此選項以在圖形中新增計數圓點"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Enable to add count lines to the plot"
msgstr "啟用此選項以在圖形中新增計數折線圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Enable to add a count area to the plot"
msgstr "啟用此選項以在圖形中新增計數面積圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Enable to add count values to the plot"
msgstr "啟用此選項以在圖形中新增計數值"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Visualise how each subgroup contributes to the whole Requires one Group "
"variable plus either an X- or Y-axis variable Absolute mode stacks raw "
"counts; Relative mode rescales each stack to 0-1 or 0-100 % Common controls: "
"Transparency sets opacity, Reverse order flips the stack sequence, Line "
"width outlines area stacks, Replace N/A turns missing groups into a separate "
"slice"
msgstr ""
"視覺化各子群組對整體之貢獻。需要一個分組變項，加上 X 軸或 Y 軸變項。絕對值模"
"式堆疊原始計數；相對值模式將各堆疊重新縮放為 0–1 或 0–100%。常用控制項：透明"
"度設定不透明度，反向順序翻轉堆疊順序，線條寬度勾勒面積圖堆疊之輪廓，取代 N/A "
"將缺失群組轉為獨立區塊"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Required: Group Variable AND X- or Y-Axis Variable"
msgstr "必填：分組變項以及 X 軸或 Y 軸變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Stack heights show raw counts"
msgstr "堆疊高度顯示原始計數"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Each stack is rescaled so its total height equals 100 %"
msgstr "每個堆疊重新縮放，使其總高度等於 100%"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add stacked bars for each category using the selected proportion mode"
msgstr "使用所選之比例模式，為各類別添加堆疊長條圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add stacked areas connected across categories"
msgstr "添加跨類別相連之堆疊面積圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Treat missing groups as a separate slice"
msgstr "將缺失群組視為獨立區塊"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Format the relative scale from 0 % to 100 % instead of 0 to 1"
msgstr "將相對尺度格式化為 0% 至 100%，而非 0 至 1"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Summary layers that display the arithmetic mean of the Y variable for every "
"X (or vice versa). Requires both X and Y axes mapped. Mean can be rendered "
"as bar, line, dot, dash, area, or value. Common controls: <b>Dodge</b> "
"separates sub-groups, <b>Transparency</b> sets opacity, <b>Size/width</b> "
"changes thickness, <b>Outline</b> toggles borders"
msgstr ""
"顯示每個 X（或每個 Y）之 Y 變項算術平均數的摘要圖層。需要同時對應 X 軸與 Y "
"軸。平均數可以長條、折線、圓點、虛線、面積或數值形式呈現。常用控制項：<b>並排"
"</b>分隔子群組，<b>透明度</b>設定不透明度，<b>尺寸／寬度</b>改變粗細，<b>輪廓"
"線</b>切換邊框"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add mean bars"
msgstr "新增平均數長條圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add dashed mean lines"
msgstr "新增平均數虛線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add mean dots"
msgstr "新增平均數圓點"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add mean profile lines"
msgstr "新增平均數輪廓線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add filled mean areas"
msgstr "新增填色平均數面積圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add numeric mean labels"
msgstr "新增平均數數值標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Sets the rounding increment for the mean value; 0.1 gives one decimal, 0.01 "
"gives two"
msgstr "設定平均數數值之四捨五入增量；0.1 表示取一位小數，0.01 表示取兩位小數"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Summary layers that display the median of the Y variable for every X (or "
"vice versa). Requires both X and Y axes mapped. Median can be rendered as "
"bar, line, dot, dash, area, or value. Common controls: <b>Dodge</b> "
"separates sub-groups, <b>Transparency</b> sets opacity, <b>Size/width</b> "
"changes thickness, <b>Outline</b> toggles borders"
msgstr ""
"顯示每個 X（或每個 Y）之 Y 變項中位數的摘要圖層。需要同時對應 X 軸與 Y 軸。中"
"位數可以長條、折線、圓點、虛線、面積或數值形式呈現。常用控制項：<b>並排</b>分"
"隔子群組，<b>透明度</b>設定不透明度，<b>尺寸／寬度</b>改變粗細，<b>輪廓線</b>"
"切換邊框"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add median bars"
msgstr "新增中位數長條圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add dashed median lines"
msgstr "新增中位數虛線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add median dots"
msgstr "新增中位數圓點"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add median profile lines"
msgstr "新增中位數輪廓線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add filled median areas"
msgstr "新增填色中位數面積圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add numeric median labels"
msgstr "新增中位數數值標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Sets the rounding increment for the median value; 0.1 gives one decimal, "
"0.01 gives two"
msgstr "設定中位數數值之四捨五入增量；0.1 表示取一位小數，0.01 表示取兩位小數"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Shows variability with vertical bars or shaded ribbons. Choose <b>Range</b> "
"(min–max), <b>SD</b>, <b>SEM</b>, or <b>95 % CI</b>. Common controls: "
"<b>Dodge</b> offsets overlapping groups, <b>Width/Line width</b> adjusts "
"thickness, <b>Transparency</b> sets opacity, <b>Black lines</b> toggles "
"outlines"
msgstr ""
"以垂直誤差棒或陰影帶呈現變異程度。可選擇 <b>範圍</b>（最小值–最大值）、<b>標"
"準差（SD）</b>、<b>標準誤（SEM）</b> 或 <b>95% 信賴區間（CI）</b>。常用控制"
"項：<b>Dodge</b> 用於錯開重疊群組，<b>寬度／線寬</b> 用於調整粗細，<b>透明度"
"</b> 設定不透明度，<b>黑色邊線</b> 用於切換外框顯示"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add range error bars"
msgstr "新增全距誤差線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add SD error bars"
msgstr "新增標準差誤差線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add SEM error bars"
msgstr "新增平均數標準誤差線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "95% CI error bar"
msgstr "95% 信賴區間誤差線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add 95 % CI error bars"
msgstr "新增 95% 信賴區間誤差線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add range ribbons"
msgstr "新增全距誤差帶"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add SD ribbons"
msgstr "新增標準差誤差帶"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add SEM ribbons"
msgstr "新增平均數標準誤差帶"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add 95 % CI ribbons"
msgstr "新增 95% 信賴區間誤差帶"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Fit trend lines or statistical models and add reference or identity lines "
"for comparison. Curve fitting requires individual data points. Common "
"controls: <b>Method</b> chooses the model, <b>Line width</b> adjusts "
"thickness, <b>Dodge</b> separates groups, <b>Transparency</b> sets opacity, "
"and <b>Color</b> selects the line colour"
msgstr ""
"配適趨勢線或統計模型，並添加參考線或恆等線以進行比較。曲線配適需要個別資料"
"點。常用控制項：<b>方法</b>選擇模型，<b>線條寬度</b>調整粗細，<b>並排</b>分隔"
"群組，<b>透明度</b>設定不透明度，<b>顏色</b>選取線條顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fit a model to the data points"
msgstr "將模型配適至資料點"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add reference lines"
msgstr "新增參考線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Add identity line (y = x)"
msgstr "新增恆等線（y = x）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Reverse direction"
msgstr "反轉方向"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fine-tune the x-axis"
msgstr "微調 X 軸"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Adds a heading"
msgstr "新增標題"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Sets the range"
msgstr "設定範圍"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Positions tick marks"
msgstr "設定刻度標記位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Handle rotation, shortening and sorting"
msgstr "處理旋轉、縮短與排序"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Shorten axis labels using K for thousand, M for million, and so on"
msgstr "使用 K 代表千、M 代表百萬等縮寫來縮短軸標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Lets you edit them manually"
msgstr "讓您手動編輯標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Fine-tune the y-axis: <b>Title</b> adds a heading, <b>Limits</b> sets the "
"range, <b>Breaks</b> positions tick marks, <b>Labels</b> handle rotation, "
"shortening and sorting, and <b>Rename labels</b> lets you edit them manually"
msgstr ""
"微調 Y 軸：<b>標題</b>新增標題，<b>界限</b>設定範圍，<b>斷點</b>定位刻度標"
"記，<b>標籤</b>處理旋轉、縮短與排序，<b>重新命名標籤</b>讓您手動編輯標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Title, caption"
msgstr "標題、圖說"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Use these fields to add text to your figure. <b>Title</b> appears above the "
"plot, while <b>Caption</b> appears below"
msgstr ""
"使用這些欄位為您的圖形添加文字。<b>標題</b>顯示於圖形上方，<b>圖說</b>顯示於"
"圖形下方"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Annotation and data label"
msgstr "註釋與資料標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Label points automatically or place custom annotations anywhere. <b>Label "
"variable</b> shows each point’s value; <b>Custom annotations</b> add free-"
"form text with position controls. Common controls: <b>Size</b> adjusts text "
"height, <b>White background</b> improves legibility, colour fields accept "
"named or hex colours"
msgstr ""
"自動標示資料點標籤或於任意位置放置自訂註釋。<b>標籤變項</b>顯示每個資料點之數"
"值；<b>自訂註釋</b>添加自由格式文字並可控制位置。常用控制項：<b>大小</b>調整"
"文字高度，<b>白色背景</b>提升可讀性，顏色欄位接受顏色名稱或十六進位色碼"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Label data by variable"
msgstr "依變項標示資料"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Label variable"
msgstr "標籤變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Variable whose values will be shown next to each point"
msgstr "其數值將顯示於每個資料點旁之變項"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "White background"
msgstr "白色背景"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Custom annotations"
msgstr "自訂註釋"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Choose an overall visual style and how colours are assigned. <b>Theme</b> "
"applies a preset look, while <b>Font base size</b> scales all text. <b>Color "
"settings</b> lets you map colour to a variable, pick a palette, or enter "
"custom colours"
msgstr ""
"選擇整體視覺風格與顏色指派方式。<b>主題</b>套用預設外觀，<b>字型基準大小</b>"
"縮放所有文字。<b>顏色設定</b>讓您將顏色對應至變項、選取色板或輸入自訂顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Decide which variable drives colours and select a palette or provide custom "
"hex/named colours"
msgstr "決定哪個變項決定顏色，並選取色板或提供自訂之十六進位色碼／顏色名稱"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Choose what determines element colours"
msgstr "選擇決定元素顏色之依據"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Uniform colors"
msgstr "單一顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Coloring by Group variable"
msgstr "依分組變項著色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Coloring by X variable"
msgstr "依 X 變項著色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Coloring by Y variable"
msgstr "依 Y 變項著色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Apply separate colours in different splits"
msgstr "在不同分割中套用不同顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Here you can specify custom colors separated by commas"
msgstr "此處可用逗號分隔指定自訂顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "e.g. red, blue, #ff5733"
msgstr "例如 紅, 藍, #ff5733"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Size, margins and plot orientation"
msgstr "尺寸、邊界與圖形方向"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Control the canvas dimensions and whitespace. <b>Plot size</b> sets the "
"pixel width × height, <b>Axis padding</b> adds proportional space inside the "
"axes, <b>Margins</b> add outer whitespace, and <b>Plot orientation</b> can "
"flip X and Y"
msgstr ""
"控制畫布尺寸與空白區域。<b>圖形尺寸</b>設定像素寬度 × 高度，<b>軸內邊距</b>在"
"軸線內部增加比例空間，<b>邊界距離</b>增加外部空白區域，<b>圖形方向</b>可交換 "
"X 軸與 Y 軸"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Width and height of the exported figure in pixels"
msgstr "匯出圖形之寬度與高度（以像素為單位）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Axis padding"
msgstr "軸內邊距"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fraction of the data range to leave empty inside each axis (0 – 1)"
msgstr "在軸線內部保留之資料範圍比例（0 – 1）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Outer whitespace around the plot (pts)"
msgstr "圖形周圍之外部空白區域（單位：點）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Plot orientation"
msgstr "圖形方向"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Flip swaps the X and Y axes"
msgstr "交換選項會互換 X 軸與 Y 軸"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Flip plot"
msgstr "交換圖形軸線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Control where the legend appears and what it shows. Use <b>Position</b> to "
"dock the legend or hide it. <b>Remove title</b> hides the legend heading"
msgstr ""
"控制圖例出現之位置及其顯示內容。使用<b>位置</b>將圖例固定於某處或隱藏圖例。"
"<b>移除標題</b>可隱藏圖例之標題"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Edit the text of individual legend entries"
msgstr "編輯個別圖例項目之文字"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Order of geometries"
msgstr "幾何物件之順序"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"point: Point<br>histogram: Histogram<br>boxplot: Boxplot<br>violin: Violin "
"plot<br>count_bar: Count bar<br>count_dash: Count dash<br>count_line: Count "
"line<br>count_area: Count area<br>count_dot: Count dot<br>count_value: Count "
"value<br>sum_bar: Sum bar<br>sum_dash: Sum dash<br>sum_line: Sum "
"line<br>sum_area: Sum area<br>sum_dot: Sum dot<br>sum_value: Sum "
"value<br>barstack: Bar stack<br>areastack: Area stack<br>mean_bar: Mean "
"bar<br>mean_dash: Mean dash<br>mean_line: Mean line<br>mean_area: Mean "
"area<br>mean_dot: Mean dot<br>mean_value: Mean value<br>median_bar: Median "
"bar<br>median_dash: Median dash<br>median_line: Median line<br>median_area: "
"Median area<br>median_dot: Median dot<br>median_value: Median "
"value<br>range_errorbar: Range error bar<br>sd_errorbar: SD error "
"bar<br>sem_errorbar: SEM error bar<br>ci95_errorbar: 95% CI error "
"bar<br>range_ribbon: Range ribbon<br>sd_ribbon: SD ribbon<br>sem_ribbon: SEM "
"ribbon<br>ci95_ribbon: 95% CI ribbon<br>curve_fit: Curve "
"fit<br>stat_ellipse: Stat ellipse<br>rm_lines: RM lines<br>reference_lines: "
"Reference lines<br>identity_line: Identity line<br>point_labels: Point labels"
msgstr ""
"point：資料點<br>histogram：直方圖<br>boxplot：盒鬚圖<br>violin：小提琴圖"
"<br>count_bar：計數長條圖<br>count_dash：計數虛線<br>count_line：計數折線圖"
"<br>count_area：計數面積圖<br>count_dot：計數圓點<br>count_value：計數值"
"<br>sum_bar：總和長條圖<br>sum_dash：總和虛線<br>sum_line：總和折線圖"
"<br>sum_area：總和面積圖<br>sum_dot：總和圓點<br>sum_value：總和值"
"<br>barstack：堆疊長條圖<br>areastack：堆疊面積圖<br>mean_bar：平均數長條圖"
"<br>mean_dash：平均數虛線<br>mean_line：平均數折線圖<br>mean_area：平均數面積"
"圖<br>mean_dot：平均數圓點<br>mean_value：平均數值<br>median_bar：中位數長條"
"圖<br>median_dash：中位數虛線<br>median_line：中位數折線圖<br>median_area：中"
"位數面積圖<br>median_dot：中位數圓點<br>median_value：中位數值"
"<br>range_errorbar：全距誤差線<br>sd_errorbar：標準差誤差線<br>sem_errorbar："
"平均數標準誤差線<br>ci95_errorbar：95% 信賴區間誤差線<br>range_ribbon：全距誤"
"差帶<br>sd_ribbon：標準差誤差帶<br>sem_ribbon：平均數標準誤差帶"
"<br>ci95_ribbon：95% 信賴區間誤差帶<br>curve_fit：曲線配適<br>stat_ellipse："
"統計橢圓<br>rm_lines：重複測量連線<br>reference_lines：參考線"
"<br>identity_line：恆等線<br>point_labels：資料點標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"You can set the order of the added geometric/data layers here, similar to "
"the example shown in the text field.\n"
"The order of the layers is defined from left to right—meaning the rightmost "
"layer will be drawn on top."
msgstr ""
"您可於此處設定已添加之幾何／資料圖層的順序，如同文字欄位中所示範例。\n"
"圖層順序由左至右定義，亦即最右側之圖層將繪製於最上層。"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Layer order"
msgstr "圖層順序"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "point, boxplot"
msgstr "資料點, 盒鬚圖"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Adjust how faceted panels share scales, axes and space. <b>Scale and axis "
"settings</b> decide whether panels use the same range, which axis lines are "
"drawn and where labels appear. <b>Layout settings</b> control panel sizes, "
"the position of the highest-value table, optional marginal plots and custom "
"axis titles"
msgstr ""
"調整分面圖面板之間如何共用尺度、座標軸與空間。<b>尺度與座標軸設定</b>用於決定"
"面板是否使用相同範圍、繪製哪些座標軸線，以及標籤顯示的位置。<b>版面配置設定</"
"b>則用於控制面板大小、最高值表的位置、是否顯示邊際圖，以及自訂座標軸標題"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Choose whether facet panels share a common scale (<i>fixed</i>) or get "
"individual ranges"
msgstr "選擇分面圖面板是否共用相同尺度（<i>固定</i>），或各自使用獨立範圍"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Decide which facet panels display axis lines"
msgstr "決定哪些分面圖面板顯示座標軸線"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Control which tick-label texts are shown"
msgstr "控制顯示哪些刻度標籤文字"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Controls where the summary table of highest values is placed inside each "
"facet"
msgstr "控制每個分面中最高值摘要表的位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Allow facet panels to stretch freely along X, Y or both axes"
msgstr "允許分面圖面板沿 X 軸、Y 軸或兩者自由伸展"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Adds aggregated rows/columns at the edges of the facet grid"
msgstr "在分面圖網格邊緣新增彙總列或彙總欄"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Arrange panels when a grid variable is mapped. <b>Layout settings</b> set "
"the facet grid’s rows, columns and where the highest-values table appears, "
"<b>Scales and strip settings</b> decide whether panels share axes and where "
"the facet label strip is placed"
msgstr ""
"當分面變項被映射時，排列面板位置。<b>版面配置設定</b>用於設定分面網格的列、行"
"以及最高值表的位置，<b>尺度與標籤帶設定</b>則決定面板是否共用座標軸以及分面標"
"籤帶的位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed number of facet columns; 0 lets the layout pick automatically"
msgstr "固定分面列數；設為 0 則由版面自動決定"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed number of facet rows; 0 lets the layout pick automatically"
msgstr "固定分面行數；設為 0 則由版面自動決定"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Choose the corner where the summary table of highest values is drawn"
msgstr "選擇最高值摘要表繪製的角落位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Fixed panels share axes; free panels get independent X and/or Y scales"
msgstr "固定面板共用座標軸；自由面板則擁有獨立的 X 軸和／或 Y 軸尺度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Location of the facet label strip"
msgstr "分面標籤帶的位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Add brackets with P values to show pairwise significance.\n"
"Set colour, text size and vertical spacing, then list each comparison in the "
"table below"
msgstr ""
"新增帶有 P 值的括號以顯示兩兩比較的顯著性。\n"
"設定顏色、文字大小及垂直間距，然後在下表列出每個比較項目"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Colour and font size of the P-value text"
msgstr "P 值文字的顏色與字型大小"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Named or hex colour for the P value text"
msgstr "P 值文字的命名色或十六進位顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Font size of the P value text"
msgstr "P 值文字的字型大小"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Starting height and step between stacked brackets (data units)"
msgstr "堆疊括號的起始高度及間距（資料單位）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Initial vertical position for the first bracket"
msgstr "第一個括號的初始垂直位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Vertical gap between successive brackets"
msgstr "連續括號之間的垂直間距"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Labels of the two groups being compared"
msgstr "正在比較的兩組標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Enter the P value (e.g. 0.03) or a significance symbol (*, **, ***). <b>Tip "
"length</b> is the size of the bracket tips; <b>Bracket size</b> is the "
"horizontal width"
msgstr ""
"輸入 P 值（例如 0.03）或顯著性符號（*, **, ***）。<b>尖端長度</b>為括號尖端的"
"大小；<b>括號大小</b>為水平寬度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "P value"
msgstr "P 值"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Select the facet (group/column/row/grid) where the bracket should appear"
msgstr "選擇括號應顯示的分面（群組／欄／列／網格）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Draw manual comparison lines (e.g., <b>min–max bars</b> or custom contrasts) "
"with optional text labels"
msgstr ""
"繪製手動比較線（例如 <b>最小–最大誤差棒</b>或自訂對比），可選擇加上文字標籤"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Note: If custom Y-Axis limits are set, the starting\n"
"position for the Y-Axis start and end values must fall within the defined "
"interval"
msgstr ""
"注意：若設定自訂 Y 軸範圍，\n"
"Y 軸起始與結束值的位置必須落在所定義的區間內"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Define one comparison line with optional label, coordinates and appearance"
msgstr "定義一條比較線，可選擇標籤、座標與外觀設定"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Text shown near the line (leave empty for no label)"
msgstr "線條附近顯示的文字（留空表示不顯示標籤）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Start/end coordinates and facet location"
msgstr "起點／終點座標及分面位置"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line start on X axis"
msgstr "線條起點的 X 軸座標"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line end on X axis"
msgstr "線條終點的 X 軸座標"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line start on Y axis"
msgstr "線條起點的 Y 軸座標"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line end on Y axis"
msgstr "線條終點的 Y 軸座標"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet column (for split layouts)"
msgstr "分面欄（用於拆分版面）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet row (for split layouts)"
msgstr "分面列（用於拆分版面）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet grid cell"
msgstr "分面網格格子"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet column (RM)"
msgstr "分面欄（重複量數）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet row (RM)"
msgstr "分面列（重複量數）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Facet grid cell (RM)"
msgstr "分面網格格子（重複量數）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Line colour and label styling"
msgstr "線條顏色與標籤樣式"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Named or hex colour for the line"
msgstr "線條的命名色或十六進位顏色"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Font size of the label text"
msgstr "標籤文字的字型大小"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Vertical offset between the line and its label (data units)"
msgstr "線條與標籤之間的垂直偏移量（資料單位）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid ""
"Combine multiple plots in custom grids. <b>Arrange plots by column</b> "
"builds the top part of the layout, <b>Arrange plots by row</b> builds the "
"bottom. Specify plot IDs, relative sizes and optional common legends"
msgstr ""
"將多個圖表組合成自訂網格。<b>按欄排列圖表</b>用於構建版面上方部分，<b>按列排"
"列圖表</b>用於構建下方部分。可指定圖表 ID、相對大小及選用的共用圖例"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Comma-separated numbers that set the width of each column"
msgstr "以逗號分隔的數字，用於設定每個欄的寬度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Comma-separated IDs referencing earlier plots"
msgstr "以逗號分隔的 ID，用於參考先前的圖表"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Relative heights of plots within this column"
msgstr "此欄內各圖表的相對高度"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Optional plot labels (A, B, …)"
msgstr "選用圖表標籤（A、B、…）"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Merge legends of all plots in this column"
msgstr "合併此欄內所有圖表的圖例"

msgctxt "jaspPlotBuilder|"
msgid "Comma-separated numbers that set the height of each row"
msgstr "以逗號分隔的數字，用於設定每列的高度"

